        Selling a Duplex or Dual Occupancy Property in Brisbane
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Duplexes attract a different buyer pool, are valued differently to standard homes, and come with title and tenancy considerations that require a clear strategy before you list.
      </p>
